d# Paper Picker — Calm Writing (Retro Tab Dock)

A full-screen “paper picker” web app that feels like a retro Flash mini-game: choose a paper style, pick a color, type inside preset boxes, and export a clean PNG that’s great for **Samsung Smart Select**.

No Flash required — it’s pure **HTML/CSS/JS** and runs in modern mobile/desktop browsers.

---

## Features

### Paper + Writing Modes
- **Post-it** (3 writing boxes)
- **Notebook** (Title + Body + Signature)
- **Book Cover** (Title + Subtitle + Author)
- **Blank** (free write)

### Paper Colors (varied but calm)
- 8 soft paper colors: Ivory, Lavender, Mint, Peach, Slate, Lilac, Butter, Sky

### “Flash-like” Retro Feel
- **Wood table** background
- **CRT scanline overlay**
- **Ornate wand cursor** + wand glow trail
- Cute **stamps** (★ / ❤ / MODE) + a **LEVEL UP** pop

### Audio (Browser-safe)
- **SFX toggle** with layered sounds:
  - tap / flip / stamp / sparkle / success
- **Music selection**:
  - Off / Chill Chiptune / Lo-fi Pad / Ambient Bells  
> Audio starts only after pressing **Start** (required by browsers).

### Export
- **Export PNG** button saves the paper + text as a PNG image.

