## Mobile Tips (Samsung Smart Select)

- The app is already **full-screen paper mode**.
- For best captures:
  - Choose your paper + color
  - Type text
  - Hide the panel by tapping outside the dock
  - Use **Smart Select** to capture the paper area

---

## Controls

### Tab Dock (Bottom)
- **Paper**: Switch paper type
- **Music**: Select background music
- **Color**: Pick paper color
- **SFX**: Toggle sound effects
- **Actions**: Random / Clear / Export PNG

### Extra Interaction
- Tap/click the paper background (not inside a text field) to trigger **sparkles**.

---

## Notes / Limitations

- Audio requires a user gesture (pressing **Start**) to play.
- Export uses an SVG→Canvas technique; if export fails:
  - Try Chrome / Edge
  - Ensure the browser allows downloads

